34#ifndef _DRM_MM_H_
35#define _DRM_MM_H_
36
37#include "drm_linux_list.h"
38
39struct drm_mm_node {
40 struct list_head fl_entry;
41 struct list_head ml_entry;
42 int free;
43 unsigned long start;
44 unsigned long size;
45 struct drm_mm *mm;
46 void *private;
47};
48
49struct drm_mm {
50 struct list_head fl_entry;
51 struct list_head ml_entry;
52 struct list_head unused_nodes;
53 int num_unused;
54 kmutex_t unused_lock;
55};
56
57/*
58 * Basic range manager support (drm_mm.c)
59 */
60extern struct drm_mm_node *drm_mm_get_block_generic(struct drm_mm_node *node,
61 unsigned long size,
62 unsigned alignment,
63 int atomic);
64static inline struct drm_mm_node *drm_mm_get_block(struct drm_mm_node *parent,
65 unsigned long size,
66 unsigned alignment)
67{
68 return drm_mm_get_block_generic(parent, size, alignment, 0);
69}
70static inline struct drm_mm_node *drm_mm_get_block_atomic(struct drm_mm_node *parent,
71 unsigned long size,
72 unsigned alignment)
73{
74 return drm_mm_get_block_generic(parent, size, alignment, 1);
75}
76extern void drm_mm_put_block(struct drm_mm_node *cur);
77extern struct drm_mm_node *drm_mm_search_free(const struct drm_mm *mm,
78 unsigned long size,
79 unsigned alignment,
80 int best_match);
81extern int drm_mm_init(struct drm_mm *mm, unsigned long start,
82 unsigned long size);
83extern void drm_mm_takedown(struct drm_mm *mm);
84extern int drm_mm_clean(struct drm_mm *mm);
85extern unsigned long drm_mm_tail_space(struct drm_mm *mm);
86extern int drm_mm_remove_space_from_tail(struct drm_mm *mm,
87 unsigned long size);
88extern int drm_mm_add_space_to_tail(struct drm_mm *mm,
89 unsigned long size, int atomic);
90extern int drm_mm_pre_get(struct drm_mm *mm);
91
92static inline struct drm_mm *drm_get_mm(struct drm_mm_node *block)
93{
94 return block->mm;
95}
96
97#endif
